column1: Senior Secondary Completion and Achievement Information, 2024
The SSCAI data is intended to provide information on the programs and pathway options offered at each school.  It is not possible to use the SSCAI to derive state-wide data.
Data is provisional as at 7 December 2024.  The VCAA accepts amendments from schools to 2024 unit results and school-based assessments until late February 2025.
For schools with fewer than four students in VCE, VET, VPC or HES, the number of students is shown as < 4. The associated measures are listed as I/D (insufficient data).
